{"tid":1086944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"後巷行方便被揭發　躁漢連環反擊　風騷走人","createTime":"2019-04-01T05:23:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T07:23:49.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"61aafb9d4abd61bff7a6ab3be2213a2dccf85682","tid":1086944,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:23:12.000Z","msg":"後巷行方便被揭發 躁漢連環反擊 風騷走人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2uBvEth\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2uBvEth&d=DYYU8Ta0XMbK5ri5AdQ6jyHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=9022c934\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2uBvEth</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190401/photo/bkn-20190401115334387-0401_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190401131314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190401%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190401115334387-0401_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190401131314&h=5d360c43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n急就去廁所啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光天化日下公然在街頭「行方便」，還惡人先告狀？大埔墟有一名男子疑隨處便溺，被樓上住客揭發後大發脾氣，引起網民紛紛派嬲！<br />\n<br />\n從網民上傳至YouTube的一條靜音片段可見，星期六（30日）上午7時43分左右，一名男子步入後巷就地小解，但過程中他突然轉身，疑喝罵樓上住戶，估計是其偷偷「方便」的行徑被人揭發。<br />\n<br />\n他大發雷霆，隨手拿起身旁的膠桶猛往上扔，並「手指指」連聲責罵，隨即再在地上拾起一個紅色膠盆往上扔，最後卻離奇地流露出活潑一面，洋洋得意地向樓上揮手道別，並急步跑離現場。<br />\n<br />\n據上傳者描述，事發地點為大埔墟，他已將事件報警處理。網民紛紛認為片中男子的行為離譜︰「係咪真係急成咁呀」、「樓上條友倒盆水落去啦」、「又要威又要走，廢柴」、「還不知錯，死不悔改」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190401/photo/bkn-20190401115334387-0401_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190401131314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190401%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190401115334387-0401_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190401131314&h=0528a56b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有男子站在後巷疑就地小解。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190401/photo/bkn-20190401115334387-0401_00822_001_03p.jpg?20190401131314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190401%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190401115334387-0401_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20190401131314&h=840dc04c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子發爛並拿起膠桶（紅圈示）往上扔。（互聯網）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190401/photo/bkn-20190401115334387-0401_00822_001_04p.jpg?20190401131314\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190401%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190401115334387-0401_00822_001_04p.jpg%3F20190401131314&h=b515f73b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子再拿起紅色膠盆往上扔。（互聯網）"},{"pid":"32aca44d683edcce282fb6a64fffdb634bd33091","tid":1086944,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:30:58.000Z","msg":"倒水快靚正"},{"pid":"542ef7cdca114f813a23d8bcd48793237deec46f","tid":1086944,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:48:02.000Z","msg":"倒水 bb 彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aee5932f393317052a41064dee506bb599532aae","tid":1086944,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:54:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b0dd5187766618e12c94360f76177273443f50c","tid":1086944,"uid":18251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"係元朗見過係公廁後行痾尿添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲唔係人，係狗嚟。"},{"pid":"7ff2579558ce5f04ab1da8cb5df157ea211a74aa","tid":1086944,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1b0dd5187766618e12c94360f76177273443f50c","tid":1086944,"uid":18251,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T07:09:30.000Z","msg":"係元朗見過係公廁後行痾尿添<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢啲唔係人，係狗嚟。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T07:1